<br>
If anything, Hate Crimes laws would affect more Blacks than Whites. The vast majority of crimes between whites and blacks (Where the victim and black on white crperpetrator are of different races) are black on white crime.<br>
<br>
Hate crimes legislation as described above would tend to increase the sentences of black criminals, thus making the disparities worse, not better. <br>
<br>
<i>Obligatory disclaimer: No, I'm not saying that all blacks are criminals, or that blacks are racists, or anything else of that nature. Just that FBI statistics show that there is more black on white crime than white on black crime. This could be due to economics, social, cultural, or any number of reasons, It just happens to correlate with race because race correlates with some of these other socioeconomic factors.</i> <p><hr><center><small><b>Never give in--never, never, never, never, in nothing great or small, large or petty, never give in except to convictions of honour and good sense. Never yield to force; never yield to the apparently overwhelming might of the enemy.</b> - Winston Churchill, October 29, 1941</small><center></p><i></i></td></tr></table><br><font color=#FF0000>- </font><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse>The Safehouse</a><font color=#FF0000> - </font><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseranthallgripeswishes>Rant Hall</a> <font color=#FF0000> - </font><a href="http://www.thesafehouse.org">The Safehouse website</a><font color=#FF0000> - </font> <center><a href="http://www.guildboss.com"><img
